  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Mudd\" title=\"House Mudd\"><img alt=\"House Mudd.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/15/House_Mudd.svg/50px-House_Mudd.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/15/House_Mudd.svg/75px-House_Mudd.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/15/House_Mudd.svg/100px-House_Mudd.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Tristifer V Mudd<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Last</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Mudd\" title=\"House Mudd\"><img alt=\"House Mudd.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/15/House_Mudd.svg/50px-House_Mudd.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/15/House_Mudd.svg/75px-House_Mudd.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/15/House_Mudd.svg/100px-House_Mudd.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nTristifer of House Mudd, the Fifth of His Name</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Rivers_and_the_Hills\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King of the Rivers and the Hills\">King of the Rivers and the Hills</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Predecessor</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tristifer_IV_Mudd\" title=\"Tristifer IV Mudd\">Tristifer IV Mudd</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Successor</th><td>\nNone</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nTristifer the Last</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Mudd\" title=\"House Mudd\">House Mudd</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tristifer_IV_Mudd\" title=\"Tristifer IV Mudd\">Tristifer IV Mudd</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)<i></i></li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Tristifer V Mudd</b>, also known as <b>Tristifer the Last</b>, was the fifth <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Rivers_and_the_Hills\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King of the Rivers and the Hills\">King of the Rivers and the Hills</a> to bear that name. A monarch of the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Mudd\" title=\"House Mudd\">House Mudd</a>, and with him his royal line became extinct.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tristifer_V_Mudd&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Tristifer V became king when his father, <a href=\"/index.php/Tristifer_IV_Mudd\" title=\"Tristifer IV Mudd\">Tristifer IV Mudd</a>, was slain in battle. He was not the equal of his very capable father and soon the kingdom was overrun and the line extinguished.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tristifer_V_Mudd&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_45\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 45\">Chapter 45</a>, Catelyn V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Riverlands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<td style=\"width:30%;\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Tristifer_IV_Mudd\" title=\"Tristifer IV Mudd\">Tristifer IV</a></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Rivers_and_the_Hills\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King of the Rivers and the Hills\">King of the Rivers and the Hills</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Next known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Benedict_I_Justman\" title=\"Benedict I Justman\">Benedict I Justman</a> </b><br /><small><i><b>as <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">King of the Trident</a> </b></i></small>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403233612\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.098 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.299 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1143/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 14076/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 9620/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1435/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser funct